These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, water
1. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | water | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, dancer
1. the fisherman is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the dancer is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | fisherman | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | board-games | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | gospel |

